# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# RootLens Ver4 - Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ===== Privy (認証) =====
NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIVY_APP_ID=

# ===== Supabase (データベース) =====
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

# ===== Cloudflare R2 (ストレージ) =====
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=
R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
R2_BUCKET_NAME=rootlens-media

# ===== Redis (Docker内部) =====
REDIS_HOST=redis
REDIS_PORT=6379

# ===== Solana =====
SOLANA_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com
# JSON配列形式で秘密鍵を設定: [1,2,3,...]
SOLANA_PRIVATE_KEY=

# ===== Metaplex (Merkle Tree) =====
MERKLE_TREE_ADDRESS=

# ===== Helius (DAS API) =====
HELIUS_API_KEY=

# ===== Irys (Arweaveアップロード) =====
# devnet: https://devnet.irys.xyz
# mainnet: https://node1.irys.xyz
IRYS_ADDRESS=https://devnet.irys.xyz

# ===== RootLens Server Keys =====
# Workerの秘密鍵（JSON配列形式）
ROOTLENS_SERVER_PRIVATE_KEY=
# Workerの公開鍵（Base58形式）
NEXT_PUBLIC_ROOTLENS_SERVER_PUBLIC_KEY=

# ===== App URL =====
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
